<li class="comment_forbidden last"></li>
</ul>    </div>
  
  
</div>
<div id="node-49" class="node node-answer node-teaser clearfix" about="/answer/phantom-power" typeof="sioc:Item foaf:Document">

        <h2>
      <a href="/answer/phantom-power">Phantom Power</a>
    </h2>
    <span property="dc:title" content="Phantom Power" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span><span property="sioc:num_replies" content="0" datatype="xsd:integer" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span>
      <div class="meta submitted">
            <span property="dc:date dc:created" content="2014-03-26T16:59:45+00:00" datatype="xsd:dateTime" rel="sioc:has_creator">Updated: Tue, 2014-08-19 09:40</span>    </div>
  
  <div class="content clearfix">
    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><p>Phantom power is a 48v power supply used to power certain microphones (condenser), active DI boxes, etc. Most preamps/audio interfaces will include an on/off switch for this.</p>
</div></div></div>  </div>

